VALIDATION AND EXTRACTION TASK
───────────────────────────────────────

IMPORTANT: Before flagging any field as invalid, attempt to extract it from the full content above. Only require approval if critical data (title, content) cannot be recovered.

1. TITLE — validate length (10–200 chars) and descriptiveness; flag if generic or missing
2. CONTENT — check minimum 100 words, readability, and completeness
3. AUTHOR — if missing, extract using "by Author", "Written by", "Author:" patterns; check metadata
4. CATEGORY — if missing, infer from content topics (technology, business, lifestyle, etc.)
5. TAGS — if missing, extract hashtags or generate from key topics
6. WORD COUNT — calculate from content if missing (count actual words)
7. READING TIME — calculate: word_count ÷ 200 minutes
8. SNIPPET — generate from first paragraph if missing (100–200 chars)
9. SENTIMENT ANALYSIS — required: classify overall_sentiment, sentiment_score (-1.0–1.0), sentiment_confidence, emotional_tone, sentiment_by_section
10. CONTENT ANALYSIS — required: readability_score, completeness_score, content_type, target_audience, headings, sections, paragraph_count, list_count, link_count
11. SEO AND MARKETING — required: potential_keywords, seo_opportunities, engagement_potential, shareability_score, cta_detected
12. LANGUAGE AND TOPICS — required: detected_language, key_topics (3–10), inferred_categories

Provide all extracted values, validation status, sentiment analysis, content analysis, SEO analysis, and approval decision in your structured response.
